The biggest, spiciest ad film of the year is HERE! 
Atlee x Ranveer Singh team up with Sreeleela & Bobby Deol for the wildest cinematic explosion of action, drama, comedy & masala.

Watch the explosive trailer of AGENT CHING ATTACKS with jaw-dropping action, whistle-worthy drama, foot-tapping music, and masala so hotâ€¦ itâ€™ll set your screen on fire.

The full film premieres Sunday, October 19 exclusively on this channel.

WHAT TO EXPECT:
â€¢ Ranveer Singh in his most powerful avatar yet as Agent Ching
â€¢ Sreeleela adding spice and swagger as Agent Mirchi
â€¢ Bobby Deol unleashing chaos as Professor White Noise
â€¢ Signature Atlee scale, style & spectacle with a global A-list crew
â€¢ A brand-new version of the iconic anthem â€œMy Name is Ranveer Chingâ€

From Bhatinda to Beijing, thereâ€™s only one kingâ€¦ Ranveer Ching!

This is the BIGGEST celebration of Desi Chinese ever â€” bold, flavourful, cinematic, and guaranteed to #AagLagaDe.

About Chingâ€™s Secret - They say that to win Hindustani hearts even Chinese food became desi! And thereâ€™s only one Desi Chinese food brand that can make desi hearts beat faster â€“ Chingâ€™s. Saucy. Spicy. Sweet and sour. Hot and sour. Crunchy. Slurpy. Zesty. Schezwani. Manchurianâ€¦ Whatever be the kind of Desi Chinese your palate craves for, only Chingâ€™s can hit the spot with a perfect zing.

I â™¥ Desi Chinese!

id.title: Serangan Agen Ching | Trailer Resmi | Atlee & Ranveer Singh | Sreeleela, Bobby Deol ğŸ”¥ğŸ”¥ğŸ”¥
id.description:
Film iklan terbesar dan terpedas tahun ini telah HADIR!
Atlee x Ranveer Singh berkolaborasi dengan Sreeleela & Bobby Deol untuk ledakan sinematik terliar yang memadukan aksi, drama, komedi, & masala.

Tonton trailer AGENT CHING ATTACKS yang eksplosif dengan aksi yang memukau, drama yang memukau, musik yang menghentak, dan masala yang begitu panas... akan membakar semangat Anda.

Film lengkapnya tayang perdana Minggu, 19 Oktober, eksklusif di kanal ini.

APA YANG HARUS DIHARAPKAN:
â€¢ Ranveer Singh dalam avatar terkuatnya sebagai Agen Ching
â€¢ Sreeleela menambahkan bumbu dan gaya sebagai Agen Mirchi
â€¢ Bobby Deol melepaskan kekacauan sebagai Profesor White Noise
â€¢ Skala, gaya, & tontonan khas Atlee dengan kru papan atas dunia
â€¢ Versi baru dari lagu kebangsaan ikonik "My Name is Ranveer Ching"

Dari Bhatinda hingga Beijing, hanya ada satu rajaâ€¦ Ranveer Ching!

Ini adalah perayaan TERBESAR untuk orang Tionghoa Desi â€” berani, penuh cita rasa, sinematik, dan dijamin #AagLagaDe.

Tentang Rahasia Ching - Konon untuk memenangkan hati orang Hindustan, bahkan makanan Tionghoa pun menjadi desi! Dan hanya ada satu merek makanan Tionghoa Desi yang dapat membuat hati orang desi berdebar lebih kencang â€“ Ching's. Berkuah. Pedas. Manis asam. Panas asam. Renyah. Slurpy. Segar. Schezwani. Manchuriaâ€¦ Apa pun jenis masakan Tionghoa Desi yang Anda idamkan, hanya Ching yang bisa memuaskan selera Anda dengan rasa yang sempurna.

Saya â™¥ Tionghoa Desi!

De grootste en meest pittige reclamefilm van het jaar is HIER!

snippet.title: Baahubali: The Epic (Official US Trailer 2)
snippet.description:
In theaters worldwide October 31, 2025!

Special First Day First Show screenings in IMAX and Premium Large Formats October 29, 2025!  

TICKETS ON SALE NOW

10 years before RRR took the world by storm, master filmmaker S.S. Rajamouli redefined Indian Cinema with his two-part BAAHUBALI saga. Now, the epic tale of royalty, revenge, kings, and wars has been personally re-edited by the master himself from two films into a single unforgettable cinematic experience, with fully remastered picture and sound (and a few new surprises), so audiences can reunite to experience the euphoria the way it was intended: on the big screen.

When a lost prince (Prabhas) is rescued and raised in exile, he grows up unaware of his past. Years later, he returns to uncover the truth about his fatherâ€™s murder and his motherâ€™s imprisonment, and must rise to reclaim his place as the rightful king.

snippet.title: Nafrat Official Music Video | Darshan Raval | Sandipa D | Akshay K | Naushad Khan | Indie Music
snippet.description:
An emotionally charged composition by Darshan Raval that delves deep into the turmoil of anger, betrayal, and heartbreak. It expresses the raw pain of trusting someone who ends up breaking that very trust, leaving behind scars that never fade. Sung and composed by Darshan Raval, with heartfelt lyrics by Noor, the song beautifully blends emotion and melody to portray the darker side of love. Featuring Sandeepa Dhar, the music video powerfully captures the intensity of disappointment and the inevitable journey from love to Nafrat.

Singer & Composer : Darshan Raval
Lyrics : Noor
Music Produced and arranged by Mir Desai

en.description:
An emotionally charged composition by Darshan Raval that delves deep into the turmoil of anger, betrayal, and heartbreak. It expresses the raw pain of trusting someone who ends up breaking that very trust, leaving behind scars that never fade. Sung and composed by Darshan Raval, with heartfelt lyrics by Noor, the song beautifully blends emotion and melody to portray the darker side of love. Featuring Sandeepa Dhar, the music video powerfully captures the intensity of disappointment and the inevitable journey from love to Nafrat.

Sheeshe ki umra
Pyaale ki akhir bisaat kya
Tuta jo dil kisi ka
To hairat ki baat kya
Tuta jo dil kisi ka
To hairat ki baat kya


Sheeshe ki umra
Pyaale ki akhir bisaat kya
Tuta jo dil kisi ka
To hairat ki baat kya
Arey tuta jo dil kisi ka
To hairat ki baat kya


Hum apne liye jite hain
Humko jaha se kya
Hum khoon jigar peete hain
Humko jaha se kya
Hum apne liye jite hain
Humko jaha se kya

Humko jaha se kya
Ek raat ki hoti hai shama
Is ki hayaat kya


Sheeshe ki umra
Pyaale ki akhir bisaat kya

To hairat ki baat kya
